WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:01.520
Good evening, family.

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:04.457
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:04.457 --> 00:00:06.205
Well, we got them.

00:00:06.205 --> 00:00:21.867
I believe the prayers of the people from this channel—and you know, I know there's a lot of other people praying, but we had thousands of people praying last night at about the same time that he was turned in.

00:00:21.867 --> 00:00:24.799
And so, I think it was within the hour.

00:00:24.799 --> 00:00:29.074
So, I just want to give God some praise that prayer works.

00:00:29.074 --> 00:00:35.428
You know, it's amazing when we all come together; many hands make light work.

00:00:35.428 --> 00:00:39.954
And I'm just thankful for her healing, the wife's healing.

00:00:39.954 --> 00:00:42.629
What is it, Erica?

00:00:42.629 --> 00:00:43.657
Is that right?

00:00:43.657 --> 00:00:44.440
Erica's healing.

00:00:44.440 --> 00:00:53.588
It helps, you know, to catch the person who murdered her husband.

00:00:54.125 --> 00:01:08.240
Praise God that we found him, that there were no other lives lost in this, that the law enforcement did a good job, and that the father had courage enough to turn his son in.

00:01:08.459 --> 00:01:16.720
You know, I thought it was interesting that his heart was convicted enough that he went to his pastor and asked for help and counsel.

00:01:16.720 --> 00:01:27.439
And the pastor said, "Of course, you should turn your son in," and he held him in his room until the authorities got there because his son was trying to flee.

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:38.080
But I believe because of the prayers of the righteous, because of us praying in agreement that this would be quickly resolved, I believe prayer changes things.

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:41.724
And what an honor to be a part of this.

00:01:41.724 --> 00:01:48.880
I'm so thankful that you join me and you take prayer seriously in these last of the last days.

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:57.600
I didn't realize that today the UN was going to have their vote.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:02.040
So, they had their vote today, and I guess it was ahead of schedule.

00:02:02.650 --> 00:02:14.116
I was praying that it was going to happen during the week of the 20th—the 22nd, 23rd—that week, but they held it the day after 9/11 in the UN.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:26.959
Yesterday, I felt it so strong to pray for New York, to pray for the two-state solution and the things that would be voted upon.

00:02:26.959 --> 00:02:37.140
And there were 10 countries that refrained—that sided with Israel—and the rest of the world basically sided against them.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:44.703
If you see this list, the ones in green are the ones that voted for a two-state solution.

00:02:49.760 --> 00:03:03.795
So France, Saudi Arabia, and these other nations are going to try to bring more of a framework in the week of the 20th, 21st, 22nd, 23rd—that week.

00:03:08.939 --> 00:03:14.420
So, there's more prayer to be done, but the vote was cast.

00:03:14.420 --> 00:03:22.720
And so we see where the nations are divided: the ones that are for Israel and the ones that are not.

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:25.169
And it's pretty alarming.

00:03:25.169 --> 00:03:33.787
I guess it was 10 countries, and they were really countries that didn't have a lot of influence that stood by Israel.

00:03:35.964 --> 00:03:46.480
From what I understand, even Australia voted for a two-state solution, and Canada, and England.

00:03:46.480 --> 00:03:55.863
There were so many that I was shocked to see on that list, very disappointed in it.

00:03:55.863 --> 00:04:07.599
But this is what the Lord warned us was coming—a line that would be drawn in the sand of who is for and who is against.

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:12.068
This is an acceleration of what the Lord said: a September to remember.

00:04:12.068 --> 00:04:15.576
And boy, it has turned out to be just like the Lord said.

00:04:15.576 --> 00:04:25.369
I don't think I'll ever forget this September, ever, already for what we've seen just in the first 12 or 13 days.

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:37.022
Incredible, actually—I mean, for how fast everything has accelerated, even just in this month.

00:04:37.022 --> 00:04:39.700
But we see the vote.

00:04:39.700 --> 00:04:50.420
Thank God the United States of America stood, just like the Lord said, a Jonathan and David relationship would begin even more in the days ahead.

00:04:50.420 --> 00:04:55.059
But we see that even Mark from Canada voted against it.

00:04:55.059 --> 00:04:58.629
And this is what the Lord was warning me about Canada.

00:04:58.629 --> 00:05:11.856
I don't know why he shows me certain countries specifically over these areas to pray concerning British Columbia in the days ahead for a great earthquake, for 30,000 casualties from an earthquake.

00:05:15.726 --> 00:05:18.606
And these are the things that I've been praying over.

00:05:18.606 --> 00:05:32.990
But it's much greater than this, as I was shown in the spirit concerning George—I won't say his last name anymore, but George—and he has a lot of influence, that's what I'll say.

00:05:40.440 --> 00:05:43.806
I saw him having a meeting with the devil.

00:05:43.806 --> 00:05:57.280
And when I was caught up in the spirit, I was allowed to hear through prayer what was going to transpire in the days ahead, of how they would try to create...

00:05:57.580 --> 00:06:01.199
you know, the Bible says we wrestle not against flesh and blood.

00:06:01.199 --> 00:06:03.332
Ladies and gentlemen, I understand.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:26.720
Basically, what's happening, what I'm trying to tell you, is that the enemy is trying to come in to wreak havoc in America for a great distraction, for great turbulence to begin—civil unrest, civil wars, things that try to escalate to bring a divide in America.

00:06:31.647 --> 00:06:37.306
And when you're distracted inside, like I said with the ants coming up out of the den...

00:06:37.306 --> 00:06:50.267
and the Lord showed me specifically five major cities out of the ten, a major event that will happen all on the same day.

00:06:50.267 --> 00:06:52.844
All on the same day.

00:06:52.844 --> 00:06:54.613
Five major cities.

00:06:54.613 --> 00:07:07.280
He showed me Chicago, Philadelphia, Washington DC, New York, and Boston.

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:08.446
These were very...

00:07:08.834 --> 00:07:10.853
it was a well-thought-out plan.

00:07:10.853 --> 00:07:15.759
I cannot go into the depth of this right now.

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:17.832
The Lord will not allow me to.

00:07:17.832 --> 00:07:51.760
But I ask you as a watchman to help me pray, to help me pray for our beautiful country, that the plans of the wicked would be uncovered by law enforcement, by our Homeland Security, by our FBI, by the sheriff's department and local law enforcement, that they would see, even just have a crack, and be led by the Spirit of God concerning these events that the enemy would try to use to kill, steal, and destroy, and cause havoc in our great nation.

00:07:51.760 --> 00:07:55.240
So, I'm asking you to help me pray even more tonight.

00:07:55.240 --> 00:08:15.639
We have a lot to pray about, but praying over the repercussions of this vote, of what I've seen in the spirit concerning trying to bring forth this two-state solution, bringing forth the end times at a rapid pace—folks, we're right there.

00:08:15.639 --> 00:08:18.240
Do you all understand?

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:24.444
If the peace agreement comes and they start to build the third temple soon, look where we are.

00:08:24.444 --> 00:08:31.199
We are just right at the edge, I told you, at a waterfall edge.

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:35.279
And it seems like, as it says, labor pains upon a woman.

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:43.599
Contractions do not decrease; they increase as the baby gets ready to be born.

00:08:43.599 --> 00:08:50.592
And I told you when we got to September the 23rd, it would be the point of no return.

00:08:50.592 --> 00:08:53.279
There's no more epidural.

00:08:53.279 --> 00:08:58.733
You know, like the doctor would come in and tell your wife, "Well, you only have this window to get an epidural.

00:08:58.733 --> 00:08:59.120
Why?

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:00.034
Because it's too late.

00:09:00.034 --> 00:09:01.280
It's time to push.

00:09:01.280 --> 00:09:02.960
It's too late.

00:09:03.520 --> 00:09:05.040
You're dilated enough.

00:09:05.040 --> 00:09:06.240
The baby's coming.

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:07.700
There's no more delay.

00:09:07.700 --> 00:09:09.680
It's time for you to push.

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:22.480
" And that's what the Lord was showing me as we cross over in the next two weeks—that things would start to escalate at such a rapid pace for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:23.184
You will see it.

00:09:23.184 --> 00:09:32.709
And a lot of people I know are saying that, and they get so mad at me: "Brandon, we believe the rapture of the church is taking place on the 23rd, and you are wrong.

00:09:32.709 --> 00:09:39.520
" Well, when you're here on the 24th and the 25th, you can come back and continue to pray with me.

00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:45.460
I'm just telling you that's how bold I am about that he is not coming on the 23rd.

00:09:45.460 --> 00:10:00.320
I believe we have a great harvest and a great shaking to awaken the body of Christ, a window of opportunity for the church to bring in the lost as quickly as possible.

00:10:00.320 --> 00:10:06.399
He doesn't want that any man should perish, but all come to repentance.

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:12.579
And this is one last call, for a great shaking is coming.

00:10:12.579 --> 00:10:24.160
As I heard the angels above, from the west to the east yelling, "Woe, woe, woe, America!

00:10:24.160 --> 00:10:28.080
A great shaking is no longer coming.

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:31.279
It is here.

00:10:31.279 --> 00:10:33.392
" That's what I heard.

00:10:34.544 --> 00:10:40.631
They sounded like thunder as I was sitting, and I came out, and the Lord said, "Sit.

00:10:40.631 --> 00:10:41.982
" I have a word.

00:10:41.982 --> 00:10:45.108
" And I told my wife, "Get the recorder.

00:10:45.108 --> 00:10:49.839
We must record what the Father is about to say.

00:10:49.839 --> 00:11:03.200
" And I had an open-eyed vision of these massive angelic—I didn't see the angels, but I knew they were angels—I heard them, and I could hear the shaking, and all five voices sounded the same.

00:11:06.560 --> 00:11:15.620
But as I had an open-eye vision, I saw the clouds, and I could see the thunder and the clouds shaking.

00:11:20.151 --> 00:11:24.891
I don't know how else to describe it, how you see a cloud shaking, but this is what I was seeing.

00:11:24.891 --> 00:11:34.399
The clouds vibrated as they said, 'Woe, woe, woe, America.

00:11:34.399 --> 00:11:36.800
' And it shook.

00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:42.880
I could feel the vibrations coming off of it, and it went from west to east.

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:48.320
And I saw a great earthquake taking place in California.

00:11:48.320 --> 00:11:53.120
I saw a great volcano getting ready to go off.

00:11:53.120 --> 00:12:06.400
I saw these plots and these five major cities plus these ten, but five are worse than the other five.

00:12:06.400 --> 00:12:12.079
Okay, you have five major cities that are hit hard, and five that are not as hard.

00:12:12.079 --> 00:12:18.840
They spent most of their money on the five, and that's all.

00:12:18.840 --> 00:12:23.866
I don't feel peace; I cannot say anything else.

00:12:23.866 --> 00:12:34.639
But you must take this seriously and pray over our beautiful nation.

00:12:34.639 --> 00:12:36.507
There's a shaking to awaken.

00:12:36.507 --> 00:12:39.760
Everybody said, 'Brandon, did you see Charlie?

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:41.413
Did you see all these things?

00:12:41.413 --> 00:12:54.293
' I saw a major minister who would be taken out with a bullet, and it would be called 'the shot heard 'round the world.

00:12:54.293 --> 00:13:00.560
' The shot heard 'round the world.

00:13:02.900 --> 00:13:05.588
He said it—the Lord said it to me several times.

00:13:05.588 --> 00:13:07.336
This was in my private prayer time.

00:13:07.336 --> 00:13:10.018
He said, 'A great shaking is coming.

00:13:10.018 --> 00:13:32.649
It will try to bring fear in the hearts of men so they won't have revival in buildings—afraid to go, afraid to gather in the country, afraid to gather in public events because of what the enemy has in store to disrupt what God is doing.

00:13:33.538 --> 00:13:37.519
God is not going to try; God is going to do.

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:44.880
He is going to have a major revival, and there's no devil in hell that will hold it back.

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:55.778
But it will take us having a backbone like a crowbar to stand in the gap and say, "Thus far, Satan, and no further.

00:13:55.778 --> 00:13:57.840
" Do you understand?

00:13:57.840 --> 00:14:36.453
' So, as I saw these events taking place on college campuses, at tailgate parties with major events, a man in a green uniform in Denver, and I've seen strategic locations on the Vegas Strip where the big pyramid is, where the water fountains go off, and more events.

00:14:57.599 --> 00:14:57.839
The Lord warned me to pray over three men.

00:14:57.839 --> 00:14:59.146
It's not just one; it's three.

00:15:01.720 --> 00:15:02.020
I saw three men strategically marked.

00:15:02.020 --> 00:15:03.519
One is Don Jr.

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:07.611
, and that's why I told you you must pray for this man.

00:15:07.611 --> 00:15:13.519
It's very serious to pray a hedge around and about him.

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:15.760
It was nighttime when I saw this happen.

00:15:15.760 --> 00:15:21.470
Now, if it happens in the daytime, I don't want to help the enemy out.

00:15:21.470 --> 00:15:35.619
I'm just telling you that I know beyond a shadow of a doubt what the Lord has told me to pray and intercede for this man.

00:15:38.347 --> 00:15:38.560
He said, 'Pray for him.

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:46.817
' He tells me these things and He visits me, and I feel His presence so strong.

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:00.160
He says, 'Pray for this man.

00:16:13.400 --> 00:16:13.760
Pray for leaders in the church.

00:16:13.760 --> 00:16:19.040
Pray for this because the enemy has a plan to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:20.754
Pray for Donald Trump's health.

00:16:20.754 --> 00:16:24.114
Pray for him, for his heart, and for his veins.

00:16:24.114 --> 00:16:29.589
' I saw this, ladies and gentlemen, before it came out in the news that they were checking all this stuff.

00:16:29.589 --> 00:16:37.960
You can't get that by the flesh; you get that by the Spirit of God.

00:16:47.040 --> 00:16:47.440
And I'm not listening to a devil; I'm listening to the Holy Spirit.

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:52.114
I have communion, I pray, and I seek His face.

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:57.387
And as you seek Him, you will find Him.

00:16:57.387 --> 00:16:59.649
If you knock, the door will be opened unto you.

00:17:14.160 --> 00:17:14.400
He said, 'I will do nothing on this earth without revealing it to my prophetic voices first.

00:17:14.400 --> 00:17:23.943
' Now, I do not consider myself a prophet; I consider myself a watchman, somebody who is called to pray.

00:17:23.943 --> 00:17:33.824
Now, I know there's other prophetic ministries on YouTube, and I bless them, but I'm just telling you, Brandon Biggs, I feel that my wife—the Lord's even told us to call our ministry Prayer Changes Things.

00:17:34.656 --> 00:17:38.423
And I couldn't call it 'Prayer Changes Things Church' because there was already one there, so I said 'Foundation.

00:17:38.423 --> 00:17:41.040
' So, I said, 'Prayer Changes Things.

00:17:41.040 --> 00:17:43.552
' That's what we're about.

00:17:43.552 --> 00:17:46.660
That's what this YouTube channel, He said, to raise up.

00:17:46.660 --> 00:17:51.336
That's what He said: 'Your main mission right now is to raise up one million people, one million prayer warriors.

00:17:53.419 --> 00:17:59.280
And through this, I will bring change through the channel in prayer across the world, and the things that I show you will prove to be accurate.

00:17:59.280 --> 00:18:03.000
' Now, I'm not saying I've always gotten everything right; I am human.

00:18:04.520 --> 00:18:07.920
And this is not here to glorify Brandon, I can assure you of that.

00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:10.493
Nobody's going to go, 'Well, Brandon, he is awesome.

00:18:10.493 --> 00:18:12.968
' It's never to glorify man.

00:18:12.968 --> 00:18:16.850
So maybe He lets you miss it, because it keeps you humble.

00:18:16.850 --> 00:18:22.280
It keeps you all cleaned up so you don't get a big head and go, 'Well, I'm such-a-much.

00:18:22.280 --> 00:18:24.320
' No, I am not such-a-much.

00:18:24.320 --> 00:18:34.240
I'm just Brandon, and I pray just like you do, and I put my clothes on just like you do, and I've got stuff I'm working through just like you do.

00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:37.324
Every single one of us has something we're working through.

00:18:37.324 --> 00:18:48.052
And anytime you think you're bigger and better—like I've seen a lot of other ministers, they try to have a big head and walk through, and you can't even get them through the doorway because their head is so big.

00:18:48.799 --> 00:18:59.587
And I've been raised around them; I see them, and they don't have time for you.

00:18:59.587 --> 00:19:03.840
They have big heads.

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:18.720
But I'm going to tell you this: it's time to deflate some egos up in here and realize that we're all human, we're all saved by grace, and all of us have a call to do something to reach the lost.

00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:22.773
Every single one of us—not one of us is better than the other.

00:19:22.773 --> 00:19:27.173
God's called every single one of you to do something big for Him.

00:19:33.520 --> 00:19:36.693
I was a janitor for fifteen years, and I was looked down upon for a lot of my life, with learning disabilities all through school and all the things that I've been through.

00:19:36.693 --> 00:19:47.966
But I can tell you, I've been at the bottom of the barrel where everybody looks at you as nothing, and then I've been at the top, and they still look at you similarly.

00:19:47.966 --> 00:20:00.000
But I'm going to tell you this: it's not about how man looks at you; it's about how Jesus looks at you and how much He has a hand on you.

00:20:00.000 --> 00:20:10.091
And you do exactly what He's told you to do, and you'll do it with great victory.

00:20:33.137 --> 00:20:33.475
I need you to be real.

00:20:33.475 --> 00:20:36.192
All this Hollywood celebrity crap is over.

00:20:36.192 --> 00:20:37.600
Do you understand?

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:39.360
Hollywood Christianity is over.

00:20:39.360 --> 00:20:43.120
It's all hands on deck, all striving for the call to say, 'Jesus, I'm here.

00:20:43.120 --> 00:20:45.360
Use me.

00:20:45.360 --> 00:20:54.600
' You could be the gardener or you could be worth billions, but either way, you're going to stand before the Father, and He's going to judge your works.

00:20:54.600 --> 00:20:58.900
He's going to say, 'You know what?

00:21:04.533 --> 00:21:06.560
You had a big ego and all these things, and all you did was for the praise of men.

00:21:06.560 --> 00:21:12.1000
' Whatever you do, in word or deed, do it all to the glory of God.

00:21:13.613 --> 00:21:23.006
I don't need somebody to tell me, 'Well done, Brandon,' because I'm looking for a 'Well done' from Him.

00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:42.752
And when I get up there, I want Him to say, 'Look, Brandon, you get to do all this in the thousand years because you kept your heart right before Me and you humbled yourself before Me all the time.

00:21:43.296 --> 00:21:46.862
You never let ego get in the way.

00:21:46.862 --> 00:21:57.600
' That's why I'm continually looking for ways that I can sow in private so I can reap openly over in the thousand years.

00:21:59.000 --> 00:21:59.280
You don't understand—I've seen it.

00:21:59.280 --> 00:22:04.720
We have a lifetime where usually, if you're blessed, you live past 80.

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:07.024
So we have this ten percent to sow...

00:22:07.024 --> 00:22:15.280
this ten percent is maybe less to sow into the thousand years to reap that, but I want to sow into the thousand years.

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:27.610
What I am doing on this side of the earth right now is so that I reap a great harvest for the thousand-year reign.

00:22:28.862 --> 00:22:29.484
And yeah, you may say, 'Well...

00:22:29.484 --> 00:22:44.062
' but I'm telling you all, that's what Brandon's doing, that's what Diana's doing, and that's what we're doing when we say, 'You know what?

00:22:44.062 --> 00:22:53.360
' We may not be around the king's table on this earth or whatever, but I'm around the king's table in heaven.

00:22:53.360 --> 00:22:55.333
" Do you understand?

00:22:55.333 --> 00:22:58.586
That's what it's about to me.

00:23:07.280 --> 00:23:07.800
I want so bad for Him to say, "Well done, thy good and faithful servant," just like I believe He did with Charlie.

00:23:07.800 --> 00:23:11.460
"Well done, thy good and faithful servant.

00:23:13.547 --> 00:23:14.373
You did it.

00:23:26.253 --> 00:23:26.559
You did it.

00:23:26.559 --> 00:23:27.360
Enter into My rest.

00:23:37.867 --> 00:23:38.133
" And so, I want to encourage you all to deflate all ego, to deflate it, and just be real.

00:23:38.133 --> 00:23:41.600
When you get real with God, He will get real with you.

00:23:41.600 --> 00:23:43.580
He'll become real to you.

00:23:43.580 --> 00:23:48.160
When you get real with God, He'll become real to you.

00:23:48.160 --> 00:23:50.347
That's a better way to say it.

00:23:50.347 --> 00:23:53.671
He'll become real to your inner man, because you're not trying to be something that you're not.

00:23:53.671 --> 00:23:57.707
He sees right through it.

00:23:57.707 --> 00:23:58.720
He sees right through it.

00:23:58.960 --> 00:23:59.920
You are not pretending.

00:23:59.920 --> 00:24:21.564
You're not covering things up, and He sees through every motive of why you do it when you do it, and your heart motive of the deepest thing that you think you're covering up.

00:24:21.564 --> 00:24:31.538
Maybe even your wife or your husband doesn't see it, but the Father sees it all, and you're not fooling nobody.

00:24:31.538 --> 00:24:32.960
You're not fooling Him.

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:44.212
The motives of the heart.

00:24:58.580 --> 00:25:09.851
And that's why I say, that's why I believe David says, "Search me and know me.

00:25:09.851 --> 00:25:12.159
Create in me a clean heart, O God.

00:25:12.159 --> 00:25:13.760
" I want you to really search yourself.

00:25:13.760 --> 00:25:20.958
That's why I do it all the time.

00:25:45.919 --> 00:25:50.445
I do it.

00:25:54.200 --> 00:25:54.580
