I dedicate my life to you, Lord.

01:20:37.013 --> 01:20:38.187
I am yours.

01:20:38.187 --> 01:20:42.160
Thank you, Lord, that you forgive me.

01:20:42.160 --> 01:20:44.670
Thank you, Lord, that you cleanse me.

01:20:44.670 --> 01:20:48.039
Thank you, Lord, that you wrote my name today in the Lamb's book of life.

01:20:56.000 --> 01:20:56.340
I may stumble, Lord, and if I do, I run to you and I'll not run from you.

01:20:56.340 --> 01:20:59.439
Help me with my issues that I've had.

01:20:59.439 --> 01:21:00.520
Help me.

01:21:00.520 --> 01:21:05.874
Help me to be strong and to submit myself unto God and resist the devil and he will flee.

01:21:05.874 --> 01:21:06.868
Help me.

01:21:06.868 --> 01:21:08.068
That's what you do.

01:21:08.068 --> 01:21:10.453
You got to ask him for help.

01:21:10.453 --> 01:21:12.933
He's an ever-present help.

01:21:12.933 --> 01:21:16.959
He's an ever-present help in a time of need.

01:21:16.959 --> 01:21:25.740
He said he'll never leave you and he'll never forsake you.

01:21:25.740 --> 01:21:34.708
Lo, to the end of the earth, I will be with you always.

01:21:34.708 --> 01:21:37.520
That's what the Bible says.

01:21:37.520 --> 01:21:39.805
He's never left you.

01:21:39.805 --> 01:21:44.025
He'll never forsake you.

01:21:55.599 --> 01:22:01.690
The moment you mess up, the moment you fall down, if you mess up with sin again, you run to God when you sin; you don't run away from him.

01:22:01.690 --> 01:22:08.079
And the moment you confess your sin is not when God found out about it.

01:22:09.479 --> 01:22:10.880
He knew about it the whole time.

01:22:10.880 --> 01:22:18.080
It's the moment you got rid of it and washed it in the blood, and he doesn't remember it anymore after that.

01:22:18.560 --> 01:22:21.750
The Bible says that once you confess it, he forgets it.

01:22:21.750 --> 01:22:23.610
It's washed from his mind.

01:22:26.260 --> 01:22:27.840
You say, "Jesus, I need help with it.

01:22:27.840 --> 01:22:35.440
" And the moment you say that tonight, your past is no longer you.

01:22:41.669 --> 01:22:41.897
You become a new man.

01:22:44.790 --> 01:22:45.140
You are a new woman.

01:22:45.140 --> 01:22:46.680
You're created in Christ Jesus.

01:22:47.100 --> 01:22:48.512
You are a new creature.

01:22:48.512 --> 01:22:50.380
You're a new child.

01:22:50.380 --> 01:22:51.863
You're washed in his precious blood.

01:22:51.863 --> 01:22:54.533
And I believe that with all my heart.

01:22:54.533 --> 01:22:59.080
And if you just gave your heart to Jesus Christ tonight, we want to celebrate you.

01:23:05.520 --> 01:23:05.760
We want to give you a Bible.

01:23:05.760 --> 01:23:17.706
My wife and I, our ministry, we love to give Bibles out to new people that give their heart to Jesus Christ on our channel.

01:23:17.706 --> 01:23:20.365
You say, "Brandon, I don't have a Bible.

01:23:20.365 --> 01:23:23.307
" Well, we want to give you one.

01:23:23.307 --> 01:23:26.115
We just want to celebrate your life tonight.

01:23:26.115 --> 01:23:32.719
We want to celebrate your decision that you gave your heart to Jesus Christ.

01:23:32.719 --> 01:23:36.720
So, if you go down in the description below, there's an email address.

01:23:36.720 --> 01:23:46.423
And I want you to put in the heading of the email that just says, "I got born again and I'd like to have a free Bible.

01:23:46.423 --> 01:23:48.159
" So that's what we will do.

01:23:48.159 --> 01:23:50.978
We'll send you a Bible and we'll never solicit you.

01:23:50.978 --> 01:23:52.470
We'll never bother you again.

01:23:52.470 --> 01:23:54.320
We just want to tell you congratulations.

01:23:54.320 --> 01:23:56.719
Congratulations on your new relationship with our Lord Jesus.

01:23:56.719 --> 01:24:00.990
And I believe the best is yet to come.

01:24:00.990 --> 01:24:04.130
Now, what do you do after that?

01:24:11.360 --> 01:24:11.699
You find a good Bible-believing church.

01:24:15.496 --> 01:24:22.060
A non-denominational church is where I would go personally and tell that pastor, "I want to be water-baptized.

01:24:28.098 --> 01:24:28.355
I need to get water-baptized.

01:24:28.355 --> 01:24:32.515
I just gave my heart to Jesus on the internet and I want to be water-baptized.

01:24:33.048 --> 01:24:36.331
" There are amazing churches out there that will give you like that are non-denominational.

01:24:36.331 --> 01:24:40.400
Even my friend Billy Burke, he has a baptismal service.

01:24:41.840 --> 01:24:42.080
I didn't even know it.

01:24:42.080 --> 01:24:43.640
He does it in the ocean.

01:24:43.640 --> 01:24:47.911
I'd love to go out there and get dunked by him out in the ocean.

01:24:47.911 --> 01:24:49.199
That would be amazing.

01:24:49.199 --> 01:24:50.439
I'd do it again.

01:25:03.280 --> 01:25:04.960
I told you, you can't do it enough.

01:25:04.960 --> 01:25:08.230
It's just saying, "Jesus, I'm sold out.

01:25:08.230 --> 01:25:09.960
" Do you understand?

01:25:09.960 --> 01:25:14.680
People try to complicate this and make it all religious.

01:25:25.063 --> 01:25:25.245
It's just saying, "I'm sold out to you, Lord.

01:25:25.245 --> 01:25:26.159
Here am I, Lord.

01:25:26.159 --> 01:25:26.640
Use me.

01:25:26.640 --> 01:25:27.680
Here am I, Lord.

01:25:27.680 --> 01:25:31.439
I'm making a public declaration saying I'm sold out to Jesus.

01:25:40.933 --> 01:25:41.947
" And that's what you do with baptism.

01:25:41.947 --> 01:25:44.879
I'm just sold out to Jesus.

01:25:44.879 --> 01:25:46.120
It's just so awesome.

01:25:56.436 --> 01:25:56.658
I just want you to get excited about it.

01:26:00.788 --> 01:26:01.085
But you get plugged in there.

01:26:01.085 --> 01:26:08.860
Wednesdays and Sundays, if they've got church, go and plug yourself in there so that you can stand strong in these end times.

01:26:08.860 --> 01:26:12.970
Do not be a sheep outside of the fold right now.

01:26:12.970 --> 01:26:15.544
The wolf will come and devour you.

01:26:15.544 --> 01:26:25.520
Especially as a baby believer, you need to get into the church and get plugged in there and learn the word.

01:26:25.520 --> 01:26:27.620
Get strong in the word.

01:26:27.620 --> 01:26:33.782
Read your Bible that I bless you with every single day.

01:26:33.782 --> 01:26:35.640
Read your Bible.

01:26:48.098 --> 01:26:48.347
And as you read it, it will change you from the inside out.

01:26:48.347 --> 01:26:51.280
It will change you from the inside out.

01:26:51.280 --> 01:26:54.462
Start with maybe Proverbs or Psalms, something easier.

01:27:14.129 --> 01:27:24.800
And just read it and meditate on it and think about what God is saying about you.

01:27:27.960 --> 01:27:28.469
And as you do, I told you it would change you from the inside out.

01:27:28.469 --> 01:27:33.006
So, we want to encourage you today in your decision of making Jesus Christ your Lord and Savior.

01:27:43.479 --> 01:27:45.990
And we just want to tell you we love you.

01:27:45.990 --> 01:27:47.600
We're praying for you.

01:27:47.600 --> 01:27:51.839
Come all the time and pray with us.

01:27:51.839 --> 01:28:00.206
We do these YouTubes and broadcast live, and we pray with the people, and the Lord shows us that which is coming soon, and I believe it with all my heart.

01:28:00.800 --> 01:28:04.221
He said we could pray and change things.

01:28:25.520 --> 01:28:25.980
So, praise God.

01:28:29.387 --> 01:28:29.893
So, that was that part of that.

01:28:29.893 --> 01:28:34.228
Did that bless you all tonight, talking about that a little bit?

01:28:39.813 --> 01:28:40.124
A 7.

01:28:40.124 --> 01:28:42.639
4 earthquake right here in Russia.

01:28:42.639 --> 01:28:45.040
We had a 7.

01:28:45.040 --> 01:28:48.176
4 earthquake tonight.

01:28:58.499 --> 01:29:08.354
The Lord told us that we would start to see these the moment they tried to divide the land, and we would see major earthquakes.

01:29:15.191 --> 01:29:15.529
And it would happen in the Ring of Fire.

01:29:15.529 --> 01:29:16.542
Remember this.

01:29:31.104 --> 01:29:31.648
So, it happened.

01:29:31.648 --> 01:29:33.280
It's happening.

01:29:33.280 --> 01:29:36.720
Remember, I told you there'll be temples shaken clear to the ground in India.

01:29:36.720 --> 01:29:40.720
I told you we would see a volcano go outside of British Columbia.

01:29:40.720 --> 01:29:45.600
There will be a massive event with 30,000 people perish in the days ahead.

01:29:45.600 --> 01:29:49.194
So let's pray tonight.

01:29:49.194 --> 01:29:54.023
Who wants to go tubing now?

01:29:54.023 --> 01:29:58.719
Have I taken too much of y'all's time?

01:29:58.719 --> 01:30:02.989
How long was that, son?

01:30:02.989 --> 01:30:07.509
An hour and 14 minutes.

01:30:07.509 --> 01:30:10.480
Were there any salvations?

01:30:10.480 --> 01:30:13.336
Yes, we had some good salvations.

01:30:13.336 --> 01:30:16.639
Praise the Lord.

01:30:16.639 --> 01:30:20.422
I'm excited to hear it.

01:30:20.422 --> 01:30:28.651
I have to get a drink before we start praying.

01:30:28.651 --> 01:30:32.640
How many are here on this live?

01:30:32.640 --> 01:30:34.987
Around 500.

01:30:34.987 --> 01:30:46.187
God saved 500 people tonight who gave their heart to Jesus Christ.

01:30:46.187 --> 01:30:47.467
500 people.

01:30:47.467 --> 01:30:58.114
Amazing what the Lord would do through a little YouTube channel.

01:30:58.114 --> 01:31:18.470
So thankful for every single one of you that gave your heart to Jesus Christ tonight, all 500 or so of you.

01:31:18.480 --> 01:31:20.256
Praise God.

01:31:20.256 --> 01:31:22.398
Praise God.

01:31:22.398 --> 01:31:28.891
So, let's take communion together.

01:31:38.960 --> 01:31:42.133
And this video will stay up and it'll get lots more views than it has right now.

01:31:42.133 --> 01:32:00.318
Last night when we were praying, we had over 30,000 people praying with us at a time.

01:32:00.318 --> 01:32:01.595
30,000.

01:32:01.595 --> 01:32:05.146
That's amazing, isn't it?

01:32:05.146 --> 01:32:08.480
30,000 people.

01:32:08.480 --> 01:32:37.280
That's a huge auditorium full of people praying for the exact same thing, where many hands make light work.

01:32:37.280 --> 01:32:47.430
Isn't that awesome?

01:33:14.542 --> 01:33:14.853
Many hands make light work.

01:33:15.786 --> 01:33:20.926
And then we translate it to our other channels.

01:33:23.040 --> 01:33:27.660
We have channels all throughout the world now.

01:33:27.660 --> 01:33:42.416
We have eight, nine channels, I don't know, ten.

01:33:42.416 --> 01:33:46.703
We have a lot.

01:33:46.703 --> 01:33:53.890
It takes Braden a lot of work.

01:34:03.984 --> 01:34:05.232
I told him, I said, "Son, you work really hard.

01:34:05.232 --> 01:34:10.355
" There it is.

01:34:16.849 --> 01:34:18.155
You see all that?

01:34:34.639 --> 01:34:35.487
That's our channels throughout the world.

01:34:35.487 --> 01:34:53.760
We're preaching the gospel and we're getting people saved one soul at a time.

01:34:53.760 --> 01:35:10.177
But now the Lord said to me, he said, "Brandon, it will no longer be a fishing pole.

01:35:10.177 --> 01:35:18.620
You're going to start having a net.

01:35:18.620 --> 01:35:54.212
" So I believe we've got our net because the word came to pass because he gave us that word a couple months ago and now it's starting to happen.

01:35:54.212 --> 01:35:59.440
500 here, 500 there.

01:35:59.440 --> 01:36:03.474
It's a net.

01:36:03.474 --> 01:36:11.680
That's a big net full of people.

01:36:11.680 --> 01:36:17.892
That's no longer a fishing pole.

01:36:17.892 --> 01:36:33.296
So it used to be we'd just get a couple people saved here and there.

01:37:14.719 --> 01:37:15.172
Now we're getting what seems to be hundreds, if not thousands.

01:37:25.909 --> 01:37:26.179
So isn't that wonderful?

01:37:26.179 --> 01:37:27.409
Jesus is so wonderful.

01:37:27.409 --> 01:37:40.765
I'm so glad you'd come and watch this and just be a part of our broadcast every time we do this.

01:37:40.765 --> 01:37:42.933
It's such a blessing.

01:37:42.933 --> 01:37:45.013
We take communion and pray.

01:37:45.013 --> 01:37:49.700
We take communion before we pray here.

01:37:55.071 --> 01:37:56.087
And I want you to take communion with me.

01:37:56.087 --> 01:38:01.159
And you're new here.

01:39:44.880 --> 01:39:45.453
We take communion.

01:39:45.453 --> 01:40:06.620
And I do it differently than probably what the Catholic Church does it or anybody else.

01:40:06.620 --> 01:40:44.996
I just do it the way this is right to me.

01:40:44.996 --> 01:40:48.950
Okay.

01:41:46.200 --> 01:41:47.120
So, Father, we lift up this body before you and we thank you, Lord, that you were wounded for our transgressions.

01:41:50.502 --> 01:41:50.811
You were bruised for our iniquities.

01:41:50.811 --> 01:42:01.910
The chastisement of our peace was upon you.

01:42:23.549 --> 01:42:24.816
And with your stripes, Lord, we are healed.

01:42:24.816 --> 01:43:15.183
And Father, we're so grateful that you took all that on the cross for us.

01:43:15.183 --> 01:43:20.239
And I believe that this is the meal that heals.

01:43:21.640 --> 01:43:29.450
The more you take this, I believe in the power of the covenant.

01:43:29.450 --> 01:43:36.520
This is a covenant that he said that we don't have to walk in sickness and disease.

01:43:36.520 --> 01:43:37.690
Do you understand?

01:43:37.690 --> 01:43:56.995
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in health, wholeness, and wealth.

01:43:56.995 --> 01:44:55.626
Mentally, emotionally, physically, financially, you don't have to be broke, busted, and disgusted in your life anymore.

01:44:55.626 --> 01:45:18.755
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory in every area of your life.

01:45:18.755 --> 01:45:38.760
There's nothing too big and there's nothing too small.

01:45:38.760 --> 01:45:54.550
Jesus Christ paid the price for it all.

01:45:54.560 --> 01:46:11.327
So, Father, we thank you, Lord, for the body.

01:46:15.920 --> 01:46:19.440
We thank you, Lord, that you took all that for us.

01:46:19.440 --> 01:46:23.405
And we take this in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:46:23.405 --> 01:46:26.777
And we call ourselves healed and whole and well in Jesus' name.

01:46:26.777 --> 01:46:33.166
Don't flippantly just take it and go, 'Well, you know, it's just a wafer of juice.

01:46:33.166 --> 01:46:35.828
' No, it represents something.

01:46:44.350 --> 01:46:44.600
It's Jesus's sacrifice.

01:46:44.600 --> 01:46:49.600
You're recognizing, taking it by faith, 'I'm healed.

01:47:05.040 --> 01:47:05.280
I'm whole.

01:47:09.627 --> 01:47:09.893
I'm well.

01:47:09.893 --> 01:47:14.897
' And we take the blood right now in the name of Jesus.

01:47:14.897 --> 01:47:17.839
We thank you, Father, for the blood.

01:47:31.119 --> 01:47:32.399
And we make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

01:47:32.399 --> 01:47:42.880
We apply the blood of Jesus over us from the top of our head to the soles of our feet.

01:47:51.422 --> 01:48:00.920
And we thank you, Lord, that the blood of Jesus Christ covers us all around this room, all around this house, all around my children, all around my wife, that no weapon formed against us would prosper.

01:48:00.920 --> 01:48:04.800
We thank you, Lord, for the blood of Jesus, Father.

01:48:12.239 --> 01:48:12.515
And we thank you, Lord, that we can pray and we see into the spirit.

01:48:12.515 --> 01:48:15.259
We know what's coming because, Father, you show us.

01:48:15.259 --> 01:48:17.943
We're not ever to be caught off guard.

01:48:17.943 --> 01:48:31.359
We plead the blood over our eyes, our spiritual eyes, and over us, Father, that we're uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force or any kind of familiar spirit trying to snare us in any way.

01:48:31.359 --> 01:48:36.069
Thank you, Lord, that we hear clearly what's coming in Jesus' name.

01:48:36.069 --> 01:48:36.663
Amen.

01:48:36.663 --> 01:48:37.180
Amen.

01:48:46.669 --> 01:48:47.179
And amen.

01:48:47.179 --> 01:48:51.108
We plead the blood over our sin.

01:48:51.108 --> 01:48:52.846
Thank you, Lord.

01:48:52.846 --> 01:48:54.980
Now, that's what I do.

01:48:57.679 --> 01:48:58.216
And then we pray.

01:48:58.216 --> 01:49:01.440
I call it going tubing.

01:49:01.440 --> 01:49:06.949
We'll pray for about an hour, I think.

01:49:15.600 --> 01:49:15.769
Is that all right?

01:49:15.769 --> 01:49:16.781
Tell me about an hour.

01:49:30.933 --> 01:49:31.315
I think we'll pray about—well, a sweet hour of prayer.

01:49:32.400 --> 01:49:36.999
I told him a word about Jesus coming and then I'll give him this and then we'll go.

01:49:36.999 --> 01:49:39.897
And Father, I thank you, Lord, right now.

01:49:39.897 --> 01:49:44.000
We just worship you.

01:49:44.000 --> 01:49:45.733
We glorify your name.

01:49:45.733 --> 01:49:51.680
Thank you, Lord, for finding the guy with the gun.

01:49:51.680 --> 01:49:58.509
Thank you, Lord, that you brought him in.

01:49:58.509 --> 01:50:03.332
Thank you, Lord, that you worked on that heart today.

01:50:03.332 --> 01:50:05.782
That you worked on the heart this morning.

01:50:05.782 --> 01:50:15.029
That you brought his dad before the pastor and the pastor told him, 'You need to turn that boy in.

01:50:15.029 --> 01:50:19.119
' And Father, it was you that did that.

01:50:49.520 --> 01:50:50.440
The dad could have hid him and put him in the back somewhere and did something with him.

01:50:55.640 --> 01:50:56.320
But Father, you worked on our behalf and you went before us through prayer.

01:51:23.679 --> 01:51:25.674
And we thank you, Father, that you exposed the darkness and you will bring forth justice and you'll bring forth healing to Erica.

01:51:25.674 --> 01:51:37.451
We thank you, Lord, for the children tonight as they're missing their father.

01:51:37.451 --> 01:51:50.251
Father, you're the ultimate Father and you step in and you give them comfort in their grieving.

01:51:50.251 --> 01:52:00.734
I thank you, Father, that you bring comfort to Erica.

01:52:05.840 --> 01:52:23.466
And Father, you bring comfort to the children, to their parents, to the grandparents, whoever's still alive—his cousins or his aunts, his uncles, whoever.

01:52:23.466 --> 01:52:36.176
Father, we thank you, Lord, that there's comfort over that family right now in their time of darkness.

01:52:36.176 --> 01:53:02.877
There's so many other people that are represented here that may not be a public figure, but they're going through something, Father, and they're hurting and they're grieving just like that.

01:53:02.877 --> 01:53:12.920
They lost somebody in a tragic car accident.

01:53:30.891 --> 01:53:31.337
Maybe their husband or their wife didn't make it home from work today.

01:53:31.337 --> 01:53:39.589
Whatever it may be, Father, they may be at home right now and they just got a divorce letter.

01:53:39.599 --> 01:53:48.971
They just got served divorce papers today and they're not knowing how they're going to salvage their life because they just lost their spouse through divorce.

01:53:48.971 --> 01:53:55.479
But Father, I know that you're the God that will turn it on a dime.

01:54:03.599 --> 01:54:11.239
Father, I know that in the midst of the darkest hour, when they're walking through that valley of the shadow of death, you said we would fear no evil, for you're with us.

01:54:11.679 --> 01:54:16.000
We thank you, Lord, that your rod and your staff, they comfort us.

01:54:16.000 --> 01:54:37.417
Father, we thank you, Lord, that you said in your word that you prepare a table before us in the presence of all our enemies, and we're eating from that table right now, and nothing shall by any means hurt us because our Father loves us.

01:54:37.417 --> 01:54:43.209
He is the good shepherd and we shall not want.

01:54:43.209 --> 01:54:50.853
He is the good shepherd in our life and we shall not want any good thing.

01:54:59.013 --> 01:54:59.386
You said in your word, Lord, that you've never seen—David said, 'I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

01:54:59.386 --> 01:55:07.520
' And Father, there's many people here tonight that have need.

01:55:07.520 --> 01:55:16.160
There's so many people throughout the whole world that they're not able to pay their bills.

01:55:19.547 --> 01:55:24.360
They're not able to pay their electric, their water, their rent, their car payment.

01:55:24.360 --> 01:55:31.211
There's so many people that are going through so much right now and they're struggling financially.

01:55:42.920 --> 01:55:43.200
I thank you, Lord, that you're the God that is a God that has a cattle on a thousand hills.

01:55:43.1000 --> 01:55:54.960
Father, you said in your word that you give and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over into our bosom.

01:55:56.760 --> 01:56:10.907
Now Father, I thank you, Lord, for financial harvest for these people right now in every area of their life, that whatever they put their hands to, Father, you said that they'll be blessed.

01:56:10.907 --> 01:56:13.246
They're blessed in the city.

01:56:13.246 --> 01:56:16.120
They're blessed in the field.

01:56:16.120 --> 01:56:23.269
